d-day is a 2013 indian action thriller film co-produced by dar motion pictures and &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; entertainment private limited . the movie is directed by nikhil advani and stars arjun rampal , huma qureshi , irrfan khan , shruti haasan and rishi kapoor in the prominent roles . the film was released on 19 july 2013 to universal critical acclaim .